The paper proposes a model for multi-view time series classification that incorporates graph-based correlation matrix and a learnable channel-aware late fusion mechanism. This involves techniques from machine learning (cs.LG), artificial intelligence (cs.AI), computer vision (cs.CV), neural networks (cs.NE), and social and information networks (cs.SI).
